LTV Corp's LTV Steel Corp said itagreed to resume negotiations with the United Steelworkers ofAmerica at the local plant levels, to discuss those provisionsof its proposal that require local implementation.    The local steelworker union narrowly rejected a tentativeagreement with the company on May 14, it said.    LTV also said it agreed to reopen its offer contained inthe tentative agreement reached with the union's negotiatingcommittee as part of a plan to resolve problems through localdiscussions.                Reuter&#3;